title: Fortios: HA sync status
agents: special
catalog: network/fortigate
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the HA synchronization status of a FortiGate firewall cluster.
 It uses the FortiOS REST API HA checksum endpoint and compares the configuration
 checksum values of the cluster members.

 The service is only discovered if more than one HA member is reported.
 If the FortiGate reports an out-of-sync state or the member checksums differ,
 the service becomes CRITICAL.

 The special agent is required for this check,
 which can be configured via “FortiOS”.

discovery:
 One service is created if an HA cluster is detected.

item:
 status
